Mandip Gill https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mandip_Gill 0 Mandip Kaur Gill (born 5 January 1988) is an English actress. Her first television role came in 2012 when she was cast as Phoebe McQueen in the Channel 4 soap opera Hollyoaks. After departing the serial in 2015, Gill went on have guest roles in Cuckoo, Doctors, The Good Karma Hospital and Casualty. In October 2017, the BBC announced that Gill had been cast as a companion named Yasmin Khan in the 2018 series of Doctor Who. Mandip_Kaur_Gill ( born_5_January_1988 ) is an_English_actress .
